To create a project in Team-Work, hover over Projects on the left-side nav bar and select Add New (“ ”). Alternatively, you can select Projects from the left-side nav bar and then click the Add Project button on the following Projects page.
The Create a New Project page is broken up into sections that allow you to configure your initial project details
